256
00:09:19,117 --> 00:09:21,116
- Right.
- It's incredible, right?

257
00:09:21,117 --> 00:09:22,386
- Hello.
- Hello.

258
00:09:22,387 --> 00:09:23,587
- Hello.
- Hello.

259
00:09:23,817 --> 00:09:25,417
